lead_paragraph: DeAndre Jordan had 23 points and 14 rebounds, and the Los Angeles Clippers opened up a large halftime lead and never relented en route to a 122-106 victory over the Houston Rockets on Wednesday night.

headline.main: Jordan, Redick Lead Clippers to 122-106 Win Over Houston
headline.print_headline: Jordan, Redick Lead Clippers to 122-106 Win Over Houston
